#: dependencies.js:107
msgid ""
"Please install the required packages and try again to enable all features."
msgstr ""
"Tafadhali sakinisha vifurushi vinavyohitajika na ujaribu tena kuwasha "
"vipengele vyote."

#: dependencies.js:121
msgid "Captures the selected area of your screen."
msgstr "Hunasa eneo lililochaguliwa la skrini yako."

#: dependencies.js:122
msgid "The core OCR engine that reads text from images."
msgstr "Injini ya msingi ya OCR inayosoma maandishi kutoka kwa picha."

#: dependencies.js:123
msgid "Improves image contrast and quality for better OCR."
msgstr "Huboresha utofautishaji wa picha na ubora kwa OCR bora."

#: dependencies.js:124
msgid "Detects and decodes QR codes from the screen."
msgstr "Hutambua na kusimbua misimbo ya QR kutoka kwenye skrini."

#: dependencies.js:139
msgid "Required dependency."
msgstr "Utegemezi unaohitajika."

#: dependencies.js:153
msgid ""
"Open a Terminal and run the following command to install the missing "
"dependencies from the official repositories:"
msgstr ""
"Fungua Kituo na uendesha amri ifuatayo ili kusakinisha utegemezi "
"unaokosekana kutoka kwa hazina rasmi:"

